description:
Just a regular old wooden stick. It'll do for now, but
splinters are an increasing possibility. +5 ATK.
name: Wooden Stick

description:
It’s a snake friend! Once a simple stick,
it’s here to help!
name: Snake

description:
Novelty size. Favored by vampire hunters and
tomato gardeners everywhere.
name: Stake

description:
Snake friend in a new form. Don't mind him if he has
red around his mouth, it's actually tomato juice.
name: Snake Stake

description:
This staff contains the spirit of a snake that has
transcended a physical form into the ultimate stick. May have venom.
name: Snake Staff

description:
Your standard-looking wooden board. A bit unwieldy,
but it's got NAILS in it! +5 ATK.
name: 2x4

description:
A surfboard made for catching sick waves,
but does well for hitting dudes too. +19 ATK.
name: Bodyboard

description:
A surfboard that glows in the dark AND may not be
legal in some areas? RADICAL! +23 ATK.
name: Neon Board

description:
The ultimate surfboard, made for riding only the
gnarliest of waves. Anything else will taint it. +30 ATK.
name: "The Big One"

description:
Your fighting spirit, personified.
...you aren't quite a ifghter yet.
name: Training Aura

description:
You feel heavier, toughter, like you can take any hit.
Or at the very least, tougher ones than before.
name: Defense Aura

description:
Your... spirit feels heavier? It's hard to describe,
but it feel like you can take more of a magic beating.
name: M. Defense Aura

description:
You feel lighter on your feet than ever! Which is
good, since they kinda hurt from all the walking.
name: Speed Aura

description:
Something inside you is telling you it's your lucky
day! Time to buy a lottery ticket!
name: Lucky Aura

description:
Something inside you is burning up! Gotta keep moving,
and the the sick fires inside you be free!
name: Fire Aura

description:
Your joints feel great! Overall, you feel much more
fluid than you normally do, time to let the world see!
name: Ice Aura

description:
You tended to pick up a lot of static electricity
before, but this is just ridiculous!
name: Thunder Aura
note:
not finished! needs 2 extra attacks to be
added once equipped

description:
Finally, the purity of your inner soul is shining
through to the world. All stats up.
name: Light Aura
